
[Chinese]

	很抱歉, 我们寄出的认证信遭受送信主机的退信, 可能的原因如下:

	
	(1). 对方邮件主机没有回应或没有该位使用者

	(2). 对方邮件主机 MX 设定错误

	(3). 此位址是错误的或假造的

	(4). 对方主机不接受来自本 BBS 的信件


	请您先至个人资料里, 查明您所填的 E-Mail 位址, 并再设一次, 若有疑问请至
	SYSOP 板查询


													BBS 站 站务组敬启


[English]

	I'm Sorry, the registernation mail has been rejected by remot host, 
	there's some possible reason:

	(1). Remote host is down or no such user.

	(2). Remote host have wrong MX record setting.

	(3). This E-Mail address is incorrect.

	(4). Remove host is denying the mail sent from this BBS


	Please dobule check your e-mail address in "user-info", and try again,
	if problem still exist, please post on SYSOP for debugging, tks!


													Yours,
													BBS Staff
